nbest targets, observing strategies and instruments for the eclipse timing\nmethod. Finally, we compare the eclipse timing as a planet detection method\nwith the radial velocities and astrometry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2010 14:34:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
