h a scenario in which planet\natmospheres have suffered the effects of erosion by coronal X-ray and EUV\nemission. The erosion line is an observational constraint to models of\natmospheric erosion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2010 15:11:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2010 13:58:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-08-11"}
